data.title: Vasili Ivanovich Ryurikovich III (1479-1533) –...
data.meta_description: Russian Czar. He was the father of Ivan the Terrible, born to Ivan lll and his second wife Sophia Palaiologina. He succeeded his father as Czar after his death in 1505. His first wife Solomonia Saburova has not produced any heirs to the throne for over 20 years. He divorced his first wife and married Elena Glinskaya in...
